```plantuml
@startuml eProsima_Integration-Service

participant "Client Application" as Client
participant "Integration Service" as IS
participant "System Handle (Fast DDS)" as FastDDS
participant "System Handle (ROS2)" as ROS2
participant "JSON-XTypes Converter" as Converter

Client -> IS : Publish Data (JSON)
IS -> Converter : Convert JSON to DynamicData
Converter --> IS : DynamicData
IS -> FastDDS : Route Data (DynamicData)
FastDDS -> ROS2 : Transmit Data (Middleware format)
ROS2 -> IS : Receive Data (Middleware format)
IS -> Converter : Convert DynamicData to JSON
Converter --> IS : JSON
IS -> Client : Deliver Data (JSON)

@enduml
```